WEBVTT

00:14:29.480 --> 00:14:33.136
and how in many cases
these forms of violence

00:14:33.160 --> 00:14:38.656
occur from family members
and people that they know,

00:14:38.680 --> 00:14:41.256
who in fact may be working for them.

00:14:41.280 --> 00:14:44.696
And frequently these cases
are not adjudicated.

00:14:44.720 --> 00:14:46.696
I meet disabled people

00:14:46.720 --> 00:14:51.376
who have been offered jobs by businesses

00:14:51.400 --> 00:14:54.776
because they live in a country
where there's a quota system,

00:14:54.800 --> 00:14:57.336
and in order to avoid a fine,

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:59.616
they will hire you

00:14:59.640 --> 00:15:00.896
and then tell you,